src:
Foto: Gaya Liburan si Dokter Gigi Tampan
03 Nov 2019, 23:10 by Syanti Mustika



Ladies, namanya Felipe Rossi seorang dokter gigi Brasil yang punya visi mulia dalam memanfaatkan keahliannya. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Dia sering bepergian ke pedalaman demi membantu orang-orang mengenai kesehatan mulut dan gigi. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Namun dibalik kesibukannya, dia juga sempat mengabadikan momen jalan-jalannya. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Menikmati waktu di pantai saat berkunjung ke Ciudad de la Costa, Uruguay. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Berfoto bersama anak-anak Amazon. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Di waktu luangnya dia juga kayaking di Alagoas, Brasil. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Dia juga bisa bergaya kekinian. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)



Bersama kekasihnya di Uruguay. (drfeliperossi/Instagram)


Brasilia - Felipe Rossi merupakan dokter gigi kondang asal Brasil. Di balik profesinya sebagai praktisi kesehatan, dia juga rajin jalan-jalan lho.
text:
Photo: Vacation Style of the Handsome Dentist
03 Nov 2019, 23:10 by Syanti Mustika



Ladies, her name is Felipe Rossi, a Brazilian dentist who has a noble vision in utilizing her expertise. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



He often travels inland to help people with oral health. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



But behind his busy schedule, he also had time to capture the moments of his walks. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



Enjoy time at the beach when visiting Ciudad de la Costa, Uruguay. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



Take a picture with the Amazon kids. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



In his spare time he also kayaking in Alagoas, Brazil. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



He can also be contemporary. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)



With his girlfriend in Uruguay. (drfeliperossi / Instagram)


Brasilia - Felipe Rossi is a famous dentist from Brazil. Behind his profession as a health practitioner, he is also avid traveler.
